{"tid":992661,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想了結左自己","createTime":"2019-01-23T10:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T16:27:09.000Z","uid":147672,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1da01e28bdadc06ca1254cf3ba8b03c5b2b286a4","tid":992661,"uid":147672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:36:19.000Z","msg":"到底一個男人 <br />\n要有幾廢 先可以令到老婆要離開你<br />\n要有幾廢 先可以令到老婆話呢個唔係屋企 係監獄<br />\n要有幾廢 先可以令到老婆覺得繼續生活係自己身邊已經壓力大到抖唔到氣<br />\n<br />\n我自己問已經滿足佢生活上一切所需<br />\n為左佢 好努力比一個家佢<br />\n為佢計劃晒所有將來<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻 完全迷失晒方向<br />\n一直以黎都係圍繞住佢世界轉<br />\n而家連個中心都消失埋 <br />\n所有野都無晒動力 <br />\n我到底為左乜繼續生存<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d3b464cbc4f18275fb4eca91b2b6eb27904c5b","tid":992661,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6669919cb5c9425f7f1f0dd7807ec34b4bf64509","tid":992661,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d3b464cbc4f18275fb4eca91b2b6eb27904c5b","tid":992661,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:38:20.000Z","msg":"唔要叫埋餸呀"},{"pid":"a5f780e57fe823ce1edc69ea6b93a54a55c2e0ad","tid":992661,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbad49edb9f6c53661ca15d9c194c7de66f62d74","tid":992661,"uid":1515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:43:39.000Z","msg":"其實可能根本唔係你問題"},{"pid":"572c9b23e12eb0958fc8e752f821fbef69184000","tid":992661,"uid":147672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"00d3b464cbc4f18275fb4eca91b2b6eb27904c5b","tid":992661,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"多謝你既笑話"},{"pid":"9e008c85255c50db324b93c0b0dd7ef3efb